{"tid":1783104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足 可唔可以唔好嫌麻煩","createTime":"2019-12-14T13:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T14:15:00.000Z","uid":34163,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f19a35bdc99961553ba1b3c654e4bea02307d336","tid":1783104,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"每次出街食飯都要搵附近既黃店<br />\n地址唔熟要搵係會用多你既分鐘時間<br />\n但係每個人都嫌麻煩<br />\n係唔會有成效<br />\n<br />\n每次一話要搵黃鋪就有人嫌我煩<br />\n話要搵好煩 不如求其食一間<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係唔會有效<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好嫌麻煩</span><br />\n<br />\n唯有大家持續建立黃色經濟圈<br />\n成件事先有效<br />\n<br />\n係呀來來去去都係講呢d<br />\n因為到今日都有人嫌麻煩"},{"pid":"768de5708ffc1942e6e7d77368ccd91f3364bd55","tid":1783104,"uid":251769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:47:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pDiMkCu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpDiMkCu.jpg&h=406aa160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRJ7hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmRJ7hx.jpg&h=a821da85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSrVdXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSrVdXx.jpg&h=a557c3ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"984944c321acc73d34e9ceabb99036bf82e600a3","tid":1783104,"uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:59:35.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e25ce37b3e232d0d443f7aa2e34f5ee5e5a53076","tid":1783104,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"<